 * <span class="attrib">@param</span> options (HASH) keys are:
 *                       leftPane         =&gt; HTMLElement,
 *                       rightPane        =&gt; HTMLElement,
 *                       rightTopPane     =&gt; HTMLElement,
 *                       rightBottpmPane  =&gt; HTMLElement,
 *                       vDivider         =&gt; HTMLElement,
 *                       hDivider         =&gt; HTMLElement,
 */</span>
